{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/flood-forecasting-centre/about","content_id":"0e7b6299-0937-4886-80a8-3dce2c516f9f","description":"The Flood Forecasting Centre (FFC) is a working partnership between the Environment Agency and Met Office.","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><h2 id=\"summary\">Summary</h2>\n\n<p>The Flood Forecasting Centre (<abbr title=\"Flood Forecasting Centre\">FFC</abbr>) provides forecasts, data and information to support flood response in England and Wales for:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>the UK and Welsh governments</li>\n  <li>Category 1 and 2 responders</li>\n  <li>the wider responder community</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>We continuously improve our services through:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>our development programme - bringing science and research into use</li>\n  <li>working closely with our users - to understand their evolving needs</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"our-services\">Our services</h2>\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/flood-forecasting-centre-services-flood-guidance-statement/flood-guidance-statement-user-guide\">Flood Guidance Statement</a> (<abbr title=\"Flood Guidance Statement\">FGS</abbr>) is:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p>a 5-day flood risk forecast at a local authority scale</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>issued daily</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>for strategic, tactical and operational planning decisions</p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/flood-forecasting-centre-services-rapid-flood-guidance/rapid-flood-guidance-information-and-user-guide\">Rapid Flood Guidance</a> (<abbr title=\"Rapid Flood Guidance\">RFG</abbr>) is:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p>a summer service - providing short notice updates to supplement the <abbr title=\"Flood Guidance Statement\">FGS</abbr></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>issued on days with heightened flood risk</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>for supporting decision making in the 0 to 3 hour timescale</p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/flood-forecasting-centre-services-flood-outlook/flood-outlook-information-and-user-guide\">Flood Outlook</a> is:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p>a guidance forecast - showing flood likelihood for the coming month</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>issued twice a month</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>for supporting decision making in the 6 to 30 day timescale</p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>We also provide:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p>an <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://api.foursources.metoffice.gov.uk/docs/flood-guidance-statement-api-public.html\">Application Programming Interface (<abbr title=\"Application Programming Interface \">API</abbr>) for the <abbr title=\"Flood Guidance Statement\">FGS</abbr></a>  - available for developers</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>specialist hydrometeorological services for the Environment Agency and Natural Resources Wales</p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"development-programme\">Development programme</h2>\n\n<p>As well as our services, we work to improve the national capability in flood forecasting.</p>\n\n<p>We do this by:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p>bringing new science and forecasting techniques into operational use</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>developing our services to provide more accurate, targeted information</p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"user-research-and-engagement\">User research and engagement</h2>\n\n<p>We continually improve our services to ensure they meet user needs.</p>\n\n<p>We do this by: </p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p>measuring our performance through regular user feedback</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>undertaking research to inform service improvements</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>keeping engaged with our users - for example through <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/flood-forecasting-centre-services-training-and-user-engagement/flood-forecasting-centre-training-and-engagement\">open days and our user group</a></p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"flood-alerts-and-warnings-for-your-area\">Flood alerts and warnings for your area</h2>\n\n<p>The Environment Agency issues <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://check-for-flooding.service.gov.uk/start-page\">flood alerts and warnings in England</a>.</p>\n\n<p>Natural Resources Wales issues <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://naturalresources.wales/flooding/check-flood-warnings/?lang=en\">flood alerts and warnings in Wales</a>.</p>\n\n<p>The Scottish Environment Protection Agency issues <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://floodline.sepa.org.uk/floodupdates/\">flood alerts and warnings in Scotland</a>.</p>\n\n<p>The Met Office issues <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.metoffice.gov.uk/weather/warnings-and-advice/uk-warnings#?date=2020-06-02\">weather warnings for the UK</a>.</p>\n\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"Page content updated to include updates to FFC services.\r\nOutdated content on services, development programme and user engagement removed.\r\nInformation on FFC service simplified as part of overall updates to FFC website.\r\nLinks to new FFC service information and user guide pages included.\r\n","public_timestamp":"2026-04-16T15:51:34Z"},{"note":"A video introduction to the FFC has been added to the 'what we do' section.","public_timestamp":"2023-01-25T08:31:20Z"},{"note":"Edited heading Our services - update to the description of the Flood Outlook","public_timestamp":"2022-06-07T10:24:40Z"},{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2021-07-21T14:11:17Z"}],"corporate_information_groups":[{"contents":["66e7b7d6-e242-4bba-832a-caee44224d13"],"name":"Access our information"},{"contents":["2ac17710-6c01-4d45-a4bd-346ca52dff7c",{"title":"Jobs","url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/flood-forecasting-centre/about/recruitment"}],"name":"Jobs and contracts"}],"headers":[{"id":"summary","level":2,"text":"Summary"},{"id":"our-services","level":2,"text":"Our services"},{"id":"development-programme","level":2,"text":"Development programme"},{"id":"user-research-and-engagement","level":2,"text":"User research and engagement"},{"id":"flood-alerts-and-warnings-for-your-area","level":2,"text":"Flood alerts and warnings for your area"}],"organisation":"c99f2cd3-22e1-4bcf-83e5-d710d66501a3","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"about","first_published_at":"2021-07-21T15:11:17+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/flood-forecasting-centre/about","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/flood-forecasting-centre/about","base_path":"/government/organisations/flood-forecasting-centre/about","content_id":"0e7b6299-0937-4886-80a8-3dce2c516f9f","document_type":"about","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-04-16T15:51:34Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"About us","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/flood-forecasting-centre/about","withdrawn":false}],"corporate_information_pages":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/flood-forecasting-centre/about/recruitment","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/flood-forecasting-centre/about/recruitment","base_path":"/government/organisations/flood-forecasting-centre/about/recruitment","content_id":"2ac17710-6c01-4d45-a4bd-346ca52dff7c","document_type":"recruitment","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-04-16T15:30:33Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"Working for FFC","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/flood-forecasting-centre/about/recruitment","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/flood-forecasting-centre/about/accessible-documents-policy","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/flood-forecasting-centre/about/accessible-documents-policy","base_path":"/government/organisations/flood-forecasting-centre/about/accessible-documents-policy","content_id":"66e7b7d6-e242-4bba-832a-caee44224d1